topics.title: FlySky FSIA6B Receiver Communication Protocols
topics.description: The FlySky FSIA6B receiver has three types of communication protocols, including PWM and two serial protocols: PPM and IBIS.
evidence_quotes: The FlySky FSIA6B receiver has three types of communication protocols

topics.title: PPM and IBIS Connection Pins
topics.description: The PPM connection is located in the first vertical slot of the receiver, with pins for sending information to the controller and powering the receiver. The IBIS protocol has a similar pin layout.
evidence_quotes: The PPM connection is located in the first vertical slot
The rightmost pin is used to send information to the controller

topics.title: UART Serial Ports on Flight Controllers
topics.description: Flight controllers have UART serial ports with separate RX and TX lines for receiving information from the radio and sending information to the radio.
evidence_quotes: The flight controllers have so-called UART serial ports
